```python
import pandas as pd
```



```python
data["release_date"] = pd.to_datetime(data["release_date"],format = "%Y-%m-%d")
```


```python
data["year"] = data["release_date"].dt.year
```


```python
revenue_by_year = data.groupby("year")[["revenue"]].sum().reset_index()
```
